thread.title_full: Vacation Rental Pros reviewed by Gerald Whitehurst

author: Gerald Whitehurst
title: Gerald Whitehurst
text: last year, we booked at the last minute for an end of summer school vacay in st. augustine beach and we used the app to find and book a sweet property 2 blocks off the beach and we loaded up and had a blast! the property was fantastic, the beach was great and the rental process was fast and efficient! we had no problems at all and decided to book a summer vacay home again for this year already!
